{"tid":462424,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[I/A] 支那新驚 手機版PUBG-荒野行動","createTime":"2017-11-08T14:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T16:48:28.000Z","uid":64380,"like":16,"dislike":241,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"b7a3ab47be6d3755938aa6220fade3c135920128","tid":462424,"uid":64380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:10:01.000Z","msg":"唔好撚理係咪大陸廠出。<br />\n唔好撚理係咪抄H1z1 PUBG。<br />\n唔好撚理乜野手機玩唔撚到槍game啦。<br />\n總之有得玩又高質就算係咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nGame圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/08/215435_48f4c63763b17def1ce043d93420b683.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F08%2F215435_48f4c63763b17def1ce043d93420b683.jpg&h=dc71e30a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/08/215436_225fe296ca39bc3451aed8d6547a994d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F08%2F215436_225fe296ca39bc3451aed8d6547a994d.jpg&h=acc12e99&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/08/215437_d63a4c3770e18e03c481740e94e613fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F08%2F215437_d63a4c3770e18e03c481740e94e613fa.jpg&h=979bdba7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌佢gameplay果場咁岩係大霧天氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全睇唔清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n新手簡介 ：<br />\n荒野求生係同PUBG完全一樣玩法，主打100個真實玩家係個超巨型地圖互相撕殺，一開始全身乜都冇由直升機空降到地面，然後執裝埋伏等釣魚。<br />\n<br />\n地圖每隔一陣都會開始放毒氣收窄個安全區，壓迫大家既生存空間，驅使大家直面敵人，最後一個生存者係唯一贏家！<br />\n<br />\nQ1) 目前版本？<br />\nA1) 目前有IOS版同AN版，但<span style=\"color: red;\">冇得跨平台連機</span>，不過據官方消息已經安排緊兩服合併。<br />\n<br />\nQ2） 有冇vip制，課金制？<br />\nA2) <span style=\"color: red;\">暫時冇vip制</span>所以唔需要擔心住...課金只會令你可以改武器同自己外觀既skin, 冇實際用途。<br />\n<br />\nQ3) 有冇得同朋友連機？<br />\nA3) 有呀，隻game有單人參賽、雙排、多人組隊（4-5人？） ， 遊戲內建Mic, 可以同朋友一齊開咪互屌，甚至殺完人對大陸狗大叫<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">HONG KONG NUMBER 1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\nQ4) 點解咁難玩，我永遠贏唔到甚至入唔到top 10?<br />\nA4) 你廢。<br />\n<br />\nQ5) 樓主ID? <br />\nA5) 大屠人氏，識我既朋友<span style=\"color: red;\">勿擾</span>"},{"pid":"a2f9405e94bb8da4415f5dfdec20fa096bf32fab","tid":462424,"uid":64380,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:10:48.000Z","msg":"自推，打機去"},{"pid":"b24ac6cb19a8657c067b4c2d3ce7137ee727ec5a","tid":462424,"uid":64380,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:42:56.000Z","msg":"負乜評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有大陸人唔殺？"},{"pid":"45c9a46c6e8660da8e91b18da548265d6a659af9","tid":462424,"uid":103879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:43:22.000Z","msg":"好難描準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe46525887f7b770873b4601b17e9f6c492ff38","tid":462424,"uid":64380,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:45:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好難描準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇試過用左手粒開槍制？<br />\n不過手機瞄一定架啦，玩多兩玩就慣"},{"pid":"2529c6337669677455d08269e0870ca09678475d","tid":462424,"uid":116211,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T14:58:00.000Z","msg":"好好玩，配對又快<br />\n玩20場，1,2,3都拎過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要識避開人群，執完槍就去安全區，安全區最後個細到一間屋左右，2,3個人伏係地下聽聲殺人好刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4